div.p:
The other virtue which hee would have added, is [
                     〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉
                  ] Brotherly love, whereby wee embrace our Brethren, or the houshold of Faith. The last virtue is Charity, or common love, which is to be extended to all men, even to enemies.
